** Install master & workers **

curl -sfL -H 'Pragma: no-cache' https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/debian-13/install-k8s.sh | sh -


******************************************************************************************************************************

** Install headlamp + certmanage + nginx **

wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/debian-13/install-headlamp.sh
chmod +x install-headlamp.sh

## Change varialbles before run :
## EMAIL="email@luc-blanc.com"
## DOMAIN="headlamp.k8s-lab0.demo-lab.site"

./install-headlamp.sh


******************************************************************************************************************************

** Install Puls8 **

wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/debian-13/install-puls8.sh
chmod +x install-puls8.sh
./install-puls8.sh


******************************************************************************************************************************

** Install Draw.io **

wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lblanc/k8s/main/debian-13/install-drawio.sh
chmod +x install-drawio.sh
./install-drawio.sh
